Name: serverinfo
Type: ENUM
Allowed-Values: off min on
Default-Value: on
Last-Modified: 2.3.17

The server information to display in the greeting and capability
responses. Information is displayed as follows:

*off*
    no server information in the greeting or capabilities

*min*
    *servername* in the greeting; no server information in the capabilities

*on*
    *servername* and product version in the greeting; product version in
    the capabilities
